                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>A conference of American Chiefs of Mission in Near Eastern countries was held at
                    Istanbul from November 26 to 29. The agreed conclusions (see <ref target="#pg_168">page 168</ref>) embodied a ninth item entitled “Current <pb facs="1527" n="1511" xml:id="pg_1511"/> Israeli-Jordan Peace Negotiations
                    and Annexation of Arab Palestine to Jordan.”</p>
            </div>
